    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "therapy won't change the reality though. the debt is real, the faces of the people i let down are real, and the shame is just part of who i am now. it feels like the only way to actually stop being a burden is to just... stop. if i'm gone, there's no more mistake to maintain. doesn't it just seem more logical to just end the cycle of falling apart than to keep dragging everyone into my mess?",
