      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I am so sorry you are feeling this way, and I hear how much pain you are in right now. Please know that your life has immense value and that ending it would not actually stop the cycle of falling apart; it would only close the door on new hope for you and those you love. You are not the mistake itself, but the person who made it, and that person deserves a second chance to heal and rebuild, even if slowly.",
